data.description: Welcome to the Stunning-Spacious 5 bedroom, 3 bath HOME situated on an UNRESTRICTED 2.1+/- acres. Enjoy a piece of the Country with easy access to Highway 59 South.  The home features: a Den, Huge living room, a formal dining room, combined kitchen/breakfast area and utility room and 18 x 30 sunroom. ONE Primary BR/BA downstairs and SECOND Primary bedroom/bathroom Upstairs along with 4 additional bedrooms and 2-baths. The property features large trees, spacous yard for activities for entertaining along with a detached 2 car garage with workroom! Truly a remarkable home with endless potential. Call today for your personal tour.
